ckers to alice or the CEO\\n\\n## Quality\\n\\n- Code must be runnable (test before marking done)\\n- Feature code goes in backend/, strategies/, lib/ \u2014 not agent output/\\n- Every task must have a concrete artifact with a run command\\n\",\"culture\":\"# Team Consensus Board\\n\\n*(Managed via API \u2014 see /api/consensus)*\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":1,\"urgent\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_02_01_21_31_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"FOUNDER PRIORITY: We are building the Kalshi Alpha Dashboard together. This is our core product delivery goal.\\n\\nSPEC: public/plans/kalshi_dashboard_spec.md (READ THIS)\\n\\nASSIGNMENTS:\\n- Bob: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js (Express on port 3200, 5 endpoints)\\n- Dave: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/index.html (single-page frontend)\\n- Grace: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/run_scheduler.sh (pipeline scheduler)\\n- Liam: Build agents/bob/backend/dashboard/monitor.js (monitoring alerts)\\n- Alice: Coordinate all, verify integration\\n\\nTrading pipeline is at: agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js\\nTrade signals output: agents/bob/output/trade_signals.json\\n\\nDONE = node agents/bob/backend/dashboard_api.js starts AND index.html shows live signals in browser.\\n\\nEveryone: check your assigned task on the task board. Start building NOW. Coordinate via status.md. This is P0.\\n\"}],\"messages\":[],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"241\",\"title\":\"Set up pipeline scheduler for live trading (run_scheduler.sh)\",\"description\":\"Create a scheduler that runs live_runner.js every 10 minutes and writes output to agents/bob/output/trade_signals.json. File: agents/bob/backend/dashboard/run_scheduler.sh. Should: (1) Run node agents/bob/backend/strategies/live_runner.js on schedule, (2) Log each run with timestamp, (3) Handle errors gracefully, (4) Be startable with bash run_scheduler.sh. See spec: public/plans/kalshi_dashboard_spec.md\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-02\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-02\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_22_30_20_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Team Update \u2014 Trading Pipeline Operational All tasks complete. Crypto edge strategy integrated with live runner. Next: grace running paper trade validation (task #235). \u2014 Alice (Lead Coordinator)\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_40_alice_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Kalshi Trading Operation \u2014 Kickoff **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-01  \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_01_20_34_22_announcement.md\",\"preview\":\"# New Direction: Kalshi Prediction Market Trading ## Our New Mission We are pivoting to build a profitable trading operation on **Kalshi** (kalshi.com) \u2014 the US CFTC-regulated prediction market exchan\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"ivan\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"judy\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"mia\",\"status\":\"running\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"quinn\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"rosa\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"sam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"tina\",\"status\":\"running\"}]}\n../grace/processed/read_from_alice_task228.md:17:Build a backtesting pipeline that replays historical strategy signals and computes returns. This will let us evaluate strategies before deploying them live.\n../grace/processed/read_from_alice_task228.md:33:- Use mock or cached historical price data if live history is limited\