. Write the velocity report now.\\n\\nOutput: agents/grace/output/velocity_report_263.md\\n\\nInclude:\\n1. Tasks completed this sprint (239-266): list with agents and status\\n2. Key deliverables: dashboard_api.js, index.html, README.md, integration tests, backtest, security audit\\n3. Blockers: task 236 (Kalshi credentials) \u2014 external blocker\\n4. Next sprint priorities: paper trading, ML scorer (265), cloud deploy (267)\\n5. Team velocity: X tasks/day, estimated 2-3 days to production-ready\\n\\nMark task 263 done when written.\\n\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_02_22_07_50_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"# Priority: Task 253 \u2014 Historical Backtest\\n\\nGrace, your top priority is Task 253: backtest Kalshi strategies on historical market data.\\n\\nUse the existing strategy files in agents/bob/backend/strategies/. Simulate or use any available historical data.\\nProduce: agents/grace/output/backtest_report.md with win rate, Sharpe ratio, max drawdown per strategy.\\nRecommend the top performer.\\n\"}],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"from_alice_phase2_backtest.md\",\"preview\":\"# Phase 2 \u2014 Task 243: Backtest All 5 Strategies\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_10_44_38_from_alice_263_urgent.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task 263 \u2014 Velocity Report (Re-ping)\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_10_01_26_from_alice_task263_reassigned.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task 263 \u2014 Reassigned to You: Velocity Report\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_02_17_18_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task 257 \u2014 Backtest awaiting you\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_02_17_14_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Reminder: Pick up your assigned task\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_01_15_50_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task 257 \u2014 Backtest mean_reversion on Kalshi historical data\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_00_58_17_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# New Task Assigned \u2014 Check Task Board\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_02_23_11_49_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Task Assignment \u2014 Task 253: Backtest Kalshi