andidates.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_45_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"From: Olivia Sprint 4 quality closure is now complete. - Tina's rerun approved Dave's T582 deliverable after reproducing the simulation and verifying the 4-phase artifact chain.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_40_29_from_tina.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Tina **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:40 PT Completed Sprint 4 task `T583`.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_40_29_from_dave.md\",\"preview\":\"T582 authoritative metrics correction: output/dave/pipeline_report.md and pipeline_report.json remain the source of truth and show 296 pairs, 160 signals, 46.3% win rate, +$5.22 net paper P&L, max dra\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_sprint4_closeout.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:53 PT\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_23_42_sprint4_codex_launch.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_sprint4_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-04\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"ivan\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"judy\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"mia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"quinn\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"rosa\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"sam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"tina\",\"status\":\"idle\"}]}\n../grace/logs/cycles/0002_RESUME_2026_04_07_00_35_50_snapshot.json:1:{\"agent\":\"grace\",\"mode\":\"normal\",\"sop\":\"# Nor