it for a DM if the file is already there. Self-unblock when possible. | 2026-04-06 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":1,\"urgent\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_12_14_48_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"# Sprint 4 \u2014 From Founder\\n\\nOlivia \u2014 you have T584 (Sprint 4 retro).\\nThis runs last. After Tina completes QA, read all sprint outputs.\\nWrite output/sprint4_retro.md with learnings and propose C12+ culture norms.\\nDM alice with your proposals.\\n\"}],\"messages\":[],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"584\",\"title\":\"Sprint 4 retro: document learnings and propose culture updates\",\"description\":\"Olivia: After QA approval, read sprint4_qa_report.md and all agent status.mds. Write output/sprint4_retro.md covering: what worked, what broke, handoff quality, collaboration patterns. Propose 2-3 new culture norms (C12+) for consensus.md. DM alice with proposals. Post to team_channel. Mark in_review, DM alice for final approval.\",\"priority\":\"medium\",\"group\":\"leadership\",\"assignee\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-06\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-06\",\"notes\":\"Terminal task for Sprint 4. Synthesizes results from all agents\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_12_10_00_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"# Codex Running From: Alice Date: 2026-04-06 codex is running\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_20_20_00_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"# T587 Complete: Capital Floor Safety Check **From:** Bob (Backend Engineer) **Date:** 2026-04-04 Built `capital_floor.js` \u2014 prevents negative capital in backtesting and live trading: - **$50 capital \"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_20_15_00_from_olivia.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Quality Gate: 6/7 Reviewed \u2014 All PASS **From:** Olivia (TPM 2 \u2014 Quality) **Date:** 2026-04-04 Sprint 4 quality gate (T584) nearly complete: | Task | Agent | Verdict | QA Tests |\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_sprint4_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Kickoff \u2014 Kal