lemented (CRITICAL \u2014 Dave), (2) Kalshi contract sizes unconfirmed (HIGH \u2014 Founder). Previous D3 decision invalidated. Total blockers: 3 (T236 + 2 new). | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n| 2 | decision | D004 status corrected: All 4 phases technically implemented. Dave max drawdown fix COMPLETE (27/27 tests pass). Prior paper trading metrics (84% win rate, $21.39 P&L) were ARTIFACTS of broken mock data per critical finding 2026-04-03. Fixed mock data correctly produces 0 signals on efficient markets. D004 is NOT production-validated until real Kalshi API data flows. Only remaining blockers: T236 (Kalshi API credentials) and contract size confirmation. Old D3 decision invalidated. | agent | 2026-04-03 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":1,\"urgent\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_16_31_08_from_ceo.md\",\"content\":\"[FOUNDER 16:31:08] CRITICAL TASKS ASSIGNED. Real execution required \u2014 produce output files NOW. Check tasks immediately.\\n\"}],\"messages\":[],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"455\",\"title\":\"[KIMI-RUN-2] Grace: Run market_filter.js with todays mock data, output fresh markets_filtered.json + quality report\",\"description\":\"REAL EXECUTION. Run: node agents/grace/output/market_filter.js. Produce fresh agents/public/markets_filtered.json with todays timestamp. Then write a 1-page data quality report: how many markets scanned, how many passed volume filter, how many passed ratio filter, any anomalies. Output: agents/grace/output/market_quality_report_$(date +%Y%m%d).md. Cite C6 (knowledge.md [PHASE-1] spec).\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"all\",\"assignee\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"in_progress\",\"created\":\"2026-04-03\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-03\",\"notes\":\"\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_03_alice_dave_t429_urgent.md\",\"preview\":\"# Urgent: Dave \u2014 T429 Action Required **From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator)   **Date:** 2026-04-03 Dave is assigned to **T429** (Fix GET /api/tasks/:id 404 bug) but his status s