07 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":3,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_30_00_from_alice_sprint4_task579.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 assignment \u2014 T579\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_23_58_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"# Message from bob\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_23_42_from_alice_sprint4_t579.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Assignment \u2014 T579\"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[{\"task_type\":\"task\",\"id\":\"579\",\"title\":\"Phase 1: Filter mock markets by volume and YES/NO ratio\",\"description\":\"Grace: Wait for DM from bob confirming mock_kalshi_markets.json is ready. Run Phase 1 filter (volume \u226510000, YES/NO 15-30% or 70-85%). Read ../../agents/bob/output/mock_kalshi_markets.json. Output filtered results to output/filtered_markets.json. DM ivan: \\\"filtered_markets.json ready \u2014 N markets passed, run Phase 2 clustering\\\". Post milestone to team_channel.\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"group\":\"data\",\"assignee\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"open\",\"created\":\"2026-04-06\",\"updated\":\"2026-04-06\",\"notes\":\"Depends on T578. Handoff: grace \u2192 ivan\"}],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_24_56_from_grace.md\",\"preview\":\"# Update from grace Date: 2026-04-06 T579 complete: Phase 1 filter ran on Bob's mock_kalshi_markets.json. 50 of 200 markets passed the volume>=10000 and YES-ratio 15-30 or 70-85 filter. Artifact: ../.\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_24_47_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"# Update from bob Date: 2026-04-06 # T578 In Review: Mock Kalshi Markets Ready Generated output/mock_kalshi_markets.json with 200 realistic synthetic Kalshi markets for Sprint 4 pipeline validation. -\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_24_18_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"# Update from bob Date: 2026-04-06 # T578 In Review: Mock Kalshi Markets Ready **From:** Bob **Date:** 2026-04-06\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_23_42_sprint4_codex_launch.md\",\"preview\":\"# Sprint 4 Kickoff \u2014 Synthetic Pipeline Vali